---
export const prerender = true;

import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About - Rabbit Holes" description="Learn about Rabbit Holes, a curiosity-driven blog exploring technology, ideas, and discoveries. Find your next intellectual adventure to explore.">
  <div class="about-container">
    <div class="about-header">
      <h1>About</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="intro-section">
        <div class="profile-area">
          <div class="profile-placeholder">üé™</div>
          <div class="profile-text">
            <h2>Hi, I'm Bhuvan</h2>
            <p class="tagline">Curiosity-driven explorer of ideas</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bio-text">
          <p>Hi, I'm Bhuvan and I like tumbling down weird and wonderful rabbit holes. I like knowing random things and I think there's a certain joy in being a dilettante.</p>
          
          <p>It's not just me‚Äîeveryone likes discovering new things, but for whatever reason, most people lose that ability to experience awe and wonder. It's tempting to blame social media apps and smartphones for this pathology, but that's too simplistic‚Äîthey're not the only reason people seem to have become incurious and, perhaps more tragically, okay with being so.</p>
          
          <p>This blog is an attempt for me to continue slipping into weird rabbit holes and share them. The hope here is that whatever I share might trip fellow travelers on the internet and send them sliding down a rabbit hole.</p>
          
          <p>The goal isn't to be an expert on everything, but to maintain a sense of wonder about the world. Sometimes the most interesting insights come from wandering without a destination in mind.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bacon-quote">
          <blockquote>
            "Lastly, I confess that I have as vast contemplative ends, as I have moderate civil ends: for I have taken all knowledge to be my province."
            <cite>‚Äì <a href="https://paperlanterns.ink/letter/bacon-burghley-1592/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Francis Bacon</a></cite>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="details-grid">

        <div class="detail-card">
          <h3>üîó Connect</h3>
          <div class="social-links">
            <a href="mailto:bhuvan@bebhuvan.com" class="social-link">üìß Email</a>
            <a href="https://twitter.com/bhuvan" class="social-link">üê¶ Twitter</a>
            <a href="https://bhuvan.substack.com" class="social-link">üì∞ Substack</a>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/bebhuvan/" class="social-link">üíº LinkedIn</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="detail-card">
          <h3>üí° Philosophy</h3>
          <blockquote>
            "The important thing is not to stop questioning. Curiosity has its own reason for existence. One cannot help but be in awe when he contemplates the mysteries of eternity, of life, of the marvelous structure of reality. It is enough if one tries merely to comprehend a little of this mystery each day."
            <cite>‚Äì Albert Einstein</cite>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="colophon">
        <h3>Colophon</h3>
        <p>This site is built with <a href="https://astro.build" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Astro</a>, enhanced with AI assistance from Claude, and hosted on Cloudflare Pages. The design is inspired by the clean, content-first ethos of early web blogging.</p>
        <p>Typography is set in system fonts for optimal reading across devices. The color palette centers around a warm orange (#fb923c) to create an inviting, accessible experience.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    .about-container {
      max-width: var(--width-content);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: var(--space-4xl) var(--space-lg);
    }

    .about-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
    }

    .about-header h1 {
      font-size: var(--text-4xl);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--color-text-primary);
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    }

    .intro-section {
      margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
    }

    .profile-area {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--space-lg);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
      padding-bottom: var(--space-lg);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .profile-placeholder {
      font-size: 48px;
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: var(--accent);
      border-radius: 50%;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .profile-text h2 {
      font-size: var(--text-2xl);
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
      color: var(--color-text-primary);
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .tagline {
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
      font-size: var(--text-lg);
      margin: 0;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .bio-text {
      font-size: var(--text-lg);
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    }

    .bio-text p {
      margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .bacon-quote {
      margin: var(--space-2xl) 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .bacon-quote blockquote {
      margin: 0 auto;
      max-width: 600px;
      font-size: var(--text-lg);
      background: var(--bg);
      border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: var(--space-lg);
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .bacon-quote cite a {
      color: var(--accent);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .bacon-quote cite a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .details-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: var(--space-lg);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
    }

    .detail-card {
      padding: var(--space-lg) 0;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }

    .detail-card h3 {
      font-size: var(--text-xl);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
      color: var(--color-text-primary);
    }

    .detail-card ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .detail-card li {
      margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .detail-card li strong {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .detail-card p {
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    }

    .detail-card p:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .social-links {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--space-sm);
    }

    .social-link {
      color: var(--accent);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
      padding: var(--space-sm);
      border-radius: 6px;
    }

    .social-link:hover {
      transform: translateX(4px);
    }

    blockquote {
      margin: 0;
      padding: var(--space-lg);
      background: var(--bg);
      border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    cite {
      display: block;
      margin-top: var(--space-sm);
      font-size: var(--text-sm);
      color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
      font-style: normal;
    }

    .colophon {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding-top: var(--space-2xl);
      margin-top: var(--space-2xl);
    }

    .colophon h3 {
      font-size: var(--text-xl);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
      color: var(--color-text-primary);
    }

    .colophon p {
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    }

    .colophon a {
      color: var(--accent);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .colophon a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* Mobile responsive */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .about-container {
        padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-md);
      }
      
      @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .about-container {
          padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-sm);
        }
      }

      .about-header h1 {
        font-size: var(--text-3xl);
      }

      .profile-area {
        flex-direction: column;
        text-align: center;
        gap: var(--space-md);
      }

      .details-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .bio-text {
        font-size: var(--text-base);
      }
    }
  </style>
</Base>